  "text": "Ultrasound measurements of subcutaneous fat thickness and Longissimus dorsi area in live cattle can be an accurate estimator of these parameters in the carcass [CITATION_1] . Thus, the determination of subcutaneous fat thickness and muscle depth by ultrasonography could show differences in the deposition of subcutaneous fat and muscle throughout the production cycle.",
